text:
*Case Overview Pro-Sem* 

This Friday, the finance Pro-Sem will be a “how to” lesson in casing.

Come learn from the outstanding finance professor himself, Ben Iverson, about how to handle quantitative cases and what he looks for in a case. Then, get a student perspective from VCIC competition champion Adam Navar as he talks about tips for cases and case competitions.

Once again, this will be 9:30-10:45am in w208. A light breakfast will be provided. We look forward to seeing you there!
